+ Understand\nDenormalization
++ Why Denormalize?
+++ Normalized = multiple joins
++++_ Slower for analytics
+++ Denormalized = fewer joins
++++_ Faster query performance
+++ Fewer joins at query time
++ How
+++ Flatten related tables
++++_ Combine fact + dimension tables
++++_ CREATE TABLE AS SELECT with JOINs
-- Medallion Architecture
---_ Bronze/Silver: normalized
---_ Gold: denormalized for analytics
---_ BI tools, star schemas, data marts
-- Tradeoffs
---_ More storage
---_ Need to refresh when source changes
@endmindmap
